        <source>getAllMarineServiceDetails(): CM_WodMarineServiceDetailSet;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
04 September 2018	jlgma1	Bug 40275: PEL1 - Add HMS resources associated with Work Order requests to the Voyage View of JRW

*/

vars

begin
